Database → Entity → Mapper → DTO → API response
API request -> DTO -> Mapper -> Entity -> Database

----------------------------------
Frameworks need a way to create the object before filling it.
A mapper needs an empty constructor because frameworks must be able to create the mapper object automatically.
new Mapper()

-----------------------------------------
🏠 Think of Spring like a manager

Spring is like a manager that:

creates objects (beans)
stores them
gives them when needed
controls their lifecycle

So you don’t use new manually.
